Interface Constants.RabbitMQ.RoutingKey

  • Enclosing interface:
    Constants.RabbitMQ

    public static interface Constants.RabbitMQ.RoutingKey
    Constants related to the RabbitMQ routing keys.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static java.lang.String BOOK_REQUEST
      The routing key used by vehicle-service to communicate a request of booking to a vehicle, must be completed with the license plate, see String.format(String, Object...).
      static java.lang.String BOOK_RESPONSE
      The routing key used by vehicles to communicate the response of a booking request from service, must be completed with the license plate, see String.format(String, Object...).
      static java.lang.String CAN_DRIVE_REQUEST
      The routing key for vehicle-service-to-vehicles communications, must be completed with the vehicle license plate, see String.format(String, Object...).
      static java.lang.String CAN_DRIVE_RESPONSE
      The routing key used by vehicles to communicate if they can do a trip for a specific user, must be completed with the username, see String.format(String, Object...).
      static java.lang.String LOGIN
      The routing key for login request performed by clients communications.
      static java.lang.String REGISTER_REQUEST
      The routing key used by a vehicle to register itself to the vehicleService system.
      static java.lang.String REGISTER_RESPONSE
      The routing key used by the vehicleService to send back the response to the vehicle after register request
      static java.lang.String VEHICLE_ARRIVED
      The routing key used by vehicles to communicate they arrived to destination.
      static java.lang.String VEHICLE_DRIVE_COMMAND
      The routing key used by vehicle-service to communicate a drive command to a vehicle.
      static java.lang.String VEHICLE_REQUEST
      The routing key for vehicle request performed by clients communications.
      static java.lang.String VEHICLE_RESPONSE
      The routing key to communicate to the client the vehicle selected, must be completed with the username, see String.format(String, Object...).
      static java.lang.String VEHICLE_UPDATE
      The routing key used by vehicles to communicate their informations updates.
